<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<title>ニュース接触タイプ診断</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
<style>
:root {
  --bg: #f3f6fb;
  --panel: #ffffff;
  --text: #1f2937;
  --sub: #6b7280;
  --line: #dbe3ee;
  --accent: #2563eb;
  --accent-soft: #e8f0ff;
  --card-bg: linear-gradient(135deg, #fffaf0 0%, #fff2c7 100%);
  --card-line: #f0c419;
  --shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
  --radius: 16px;
}

* {
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
  margin: 0;
  font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Hiragino Sans",
    "Hiragino Kaku Gothic ProN", "Noto Sans JP", Meiryo, sans-serif;
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at top right, #eef4ff 0%, transparent 30%),
    linear-gradient(180deg, #f7f9fd 0%, #eef3f9 100%);
  color: var(--text);
  padding: 18px;
  line-height: 1.7;
}

.container {
  max-width: 760px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.panel {
  background: var(--panel);
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: var(--radius);
  padding: 18px;
  margin-bottom: 18px;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 14px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.05);
}

.title {
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: 24px;
  line-height: 1.4;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  letter-spacing: .01em;
}

.subtitle {
  color: var(--sub);
  font-size: 15px;
}

.progress-wrap {
  margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.progress-top {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--sub);
}

.progress-bar {
  width: 100%;
  height: 12px;
  background: #e7edf6;
  border-radius: 999px;
  overflow: hidden;
  box-shadow: inset 0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.06);
}

.progress-fill {
  height: 100%;
  width: 0%;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, #60a5fa 0%, #2563eb 100%);
  transition: width .25s ease;
}

.q-title {
  font-size: 22px;
  font-weight: 800;
  line-height: 1.5;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.answers {
  margin-top: 16px;
}

.answer-btn,
.nav-btn,
.share-btn,
.retry-btn,
.article-link {
  border-radius: 14px;
  transition: .2s ease;
}

.answer-btn {
  display: block;
  width: 100%;
  text-align: left;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  padding: 16px 16px;
  border: 1px solid #d5dfec;
  background: #fff;
  cursor: pointer;
  font-size: 16px;
  line-height: 1.6;
  color: var(--text);
  box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.03);
}

.answer-btn:hover {
  background: #f8fbff;
  border-color: #8ab4ff;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.answer-num {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  width: 28px;
  min-width: 28px;
  height: 28px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  background: var(--accent-soft);
  color: var(--accent);
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-right: 10px;
  vertical-align: top;
}

.nav-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
  margin-top: 16px;
}

.nav-btn,
.share-btn,
.retry-btn {
  appearance: none;
  border: none;
  cursor: pointer;
  padding: 13px 16px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.nav-btn.secondary,
.retry-btn.secondary {
  background: #eef2f7;
  color: #334155;
}

.nav-btn.primary,
.retry-btn.primary {
  background: var(--accent);
  color: #fff;
}

.nav-btn:disabled {
  cursor: not-allowed;
  opacity: 0.5;
}

.result-card {
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--card-line);
  background: var(--card-bg);
  border-radius: 22px;
  padding: 20px;
  box-shadow: var(--shadow);
}

.result-card::before {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  top: -40px;
  right: -40px;
  width: 160px;
  height: 160px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.35);
}

.result-card::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -50px;
  left: -30px;
  width: 140px;
  height: 140px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
}

.result-badge {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  display: inline-block;
  background: rgba(255,255,255,.8);
  color: #7c5a00;
  padding: 6px 12px;
  border-radius: 999px;
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 800;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  border: 1px solid rgba(181, 137, 0, 0.15);
  backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
}

.result-name {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  font-size: 28px;
  font-weight: 900;
  line-height: 1.35;
  color: #7a5800;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.result-desc {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 1;
  font-size: 16px;
  color: #4b5563;
}

.result-grid {
  display: grid;
  gap: 16px;
  margin-top: 16px;
}

.info-card {
  background: #fff;
  border: 1px solid var(--line);
  border-radius: 18px;
  padding: 16px;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.03);
}

.info-title {
  font-weight: 800;
  font-size: 17px;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.advice-list {
  margin: 0;
  padding-left: 1.2em;
  color: #374151;
}

.advice-list li + li {
  margin-top: 8px;
}

.article-link {
  display: block;
  text-decoration: none;
  background: #f8fbff;
  border: 1px solid #d8e7ff;
  color: #1d4ed8;
  padding: 14px 15px;
  font-weight: 700;
}

.article-link:hover {
  background: #eef5ff;
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.article-note {
  color: var(--sub);
  font-size: 13px;
  margin-top: 8px;
}

.share-row {
  display: flex;
  gap: 10px;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  margin-top: 16px;
}

.share-btn {
  background: #111827;
  color: #fff;
}

.share-btn:hover {
  transform: translateY(-1px);
}

.share-btn.secondary {
  background: #eef2f7;
  color: #334155;
}

.small-note {
  margin-top: 10px;
  color: var(--sub);
  font-size: 13px;
}

.hidden {
  display: none !important;
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  body {
    padding: 12px;
  }

  .panel {
    padding: 15px;
    border-radius: 14px;
  }

  .title {
    font-size: 21px;
  }

  .q-title {
    font-size: 19px;
  }

  .answer-btn {
    font-size: 15px;
    padding: 14px 14px;
  }

  .nav-row {
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .nav-btn,
  .retry-btn,
  .share-btn {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .result-name {
    font-size: 24px;
  }

  .result-desc {
    font-size: 15px;
  }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">

  <div class="panel" id="intro">
    <div class="title">5つの質問に答えて、あなたのニュースとの付き合い方をチェックしよう！</div>
    <div class="subtitle">ニュースの取り方のタイプを、あなたの回答パターンから動物キャラクターで診断します。</div>
  </div>

  <div id="quiz"></div>

  <div class="panel hidden" id="resultArea">
    <div class="title">診断結果</div>

    <div id="resultCard" class="result-card"></div>

    <div class="result-grid">
      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-title">あなたへのアドバイス</div>
        <ul id="adviceList" class="advice-list"></ul>
      </div>

      <div class="info-card">
        <div class="info-title">おすすめ記事</div>
        <a id="articleLink" class="article-link" href="#" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"></a>
        <div id="articleNote" class="article-note"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="share-row">
      <button class="share-btn" id="shareXBtn" type="button">Xでシェアする</button>
      <button class="share-btn secondary" id="copyResultBtn" type="button">結果文をコピー</button>
    </div>

    <div class="small-note">※ シェア文には診断結果と診断ページURLが入ります。</div>

    <div class="nav-row">
      <button class="retry-btn secondary" id="restartBtn" type="button">もう一度診断する</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

